videos.description: Jacob Eason find Andre Baccellia on a short pass, who then makes it through four Boise State players on the way to the end zone for a Washington touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Baccellia runs past four Broncos for TD off of Eason pass) 2019/12/21 ESHEETS

videos.headline: Baccellia runs past four Broncos for TD off of Eason pass

videos.description: Elijah Molden takes advantage of a high throw from Boise State's Hank Bachmeier and picks it off, then returns it 31 yards and Washington takes over.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Bachmeier picked off by Molden, returned for 31 yards) 2019/12/21

videos.headline: Bachmeier picked off by Molden, returned for 31 yards

videos.description: Richard Newton capitalizes off a Washington Huskies interception by scoring a touchdown from 2 yards out.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Newton pounds the rock into the end zone for 6) 2019/12/21 ESHEETS

videos.headline: Newton pounds the rock into the end zone for 6

videos.description: Washington running back Richard Newton rolls out from the Wildcat formation and throws a touchdown pass to Terrell Bynum to put the Huskies up 31-7 over Boise State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Newton throws TD pass to Bynum from Wildcat formation) 2019/12/21 ESHEETS

videos.headline: Newton throws TD pass to Bynum from Wildcat formation

videos.description: In his final game as the Washington head coach, Chris Petersen looks on as Salvon Ahmed scampers into the end zone from 12-yards out vs. Boise State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Chris Petersen looks on as Ahmed runs it in from 12-yards out) 2019/12/21 ESHEETS

videos.headline: Chris Petersen looks on as Ahmed runs it in from 12-yards out

videos.description: Molly McGrath talks to Chris Petersen as he walks off victorious in his final game as the head coach of the Washington Huskies.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Petersen walks off the field for last time as Washington coach) 2019/12/21 ESHEETS

videos.headline: Petersen walks off the field for last time as Washington coach
